---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="avatar">
    <img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="Sakshi Gupta illustration" width="100" height="100" />
  </div>

  <h1 class="name">Sakshi Gupta</h1>

  <p>I am a Product Designer based in <span class="highlight">Bengaluru, India <img src="/images/icons/india-flag.svg" alt="" class="inline-icon" aria-hidden="true" /></span></p>

  <p>Currently designing experiences at <a href="https://juspay.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="highlight">Juspay <img src="/images/icons/juspay.svg" alt="" class="inline-icon" aria-hidden="true" /></a> . And this is my tiny corner on the internet where I share my craft and the products I'm building.</p>

  <p>Reach out to me on
    <a href="https://x.com/sakshi_026" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="chip"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>DMs</a>
    or email me at
    <span class="email-wrap">
      <span class="copy-toast">Copied!</span><a href="mailto:sakshigupta9368@gmail.com" class="chip email-chip" data-email="sakshigupta9368@gmail.com"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>sakshigupta9368@gmail.com</a><svg class="copy-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"/></svg></span></p>
</section>

<script>
  const emailWrap = document.querySelector('.email-wrap');
  const copyIcon = document.querySelector('.email-wrap .copy-icon');
  if (emailWrap && copyIcon) {
    copyIcon.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      const email = emailWrap.querySelector('.email-chip')?.getAttribute('data-email');
      if (email) {
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(email);
        const toast = emailWrap.querySelector('.copy-toast');
        if (toast) {
          toast.classList.add('show');
          setTimeout(() => toast.classList.remove('show'), 1500);
        }
      }
    });
  }
</script>

<style>
  .hero { padding: var(--space-72) 0 var(--space-48); }
  .avatar {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    margin-left: -16px;
  }
  .avatar img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  .name {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  p {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-14);
  }
  p a {
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    transition: color var(--ease-default), border-color var(--ease-default);
  }
  p a:not(.chip):hover { color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 0px 5px;
    background: var(--line-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: none;
    vertical-align: middle;
    transition: background 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .chip:hover {
    background: var(--line-2);
  }
  .chip svg { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .email-wrap {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .copy-icon {
    opacity: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
  }
  .email-wrap:hover .copy-icon {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .copy-icon:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .copy-toast {
    position: absolute;
    top: -32px;
    right: 0;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(4px);
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }
  .copy-toast.show {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  .highlight { color: var(--ink); font-weight: var(--weight-medium); }
  p a.highlight { border-bottom: none; }
  .inline-icon {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 15px;
    height: 15px;
    vertical-align: -3px;
    margin-left: 2px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero { padding: var(--space-56) 0 var(--space-48); }
    .name { font-size: 18px; }
    .avatar { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-left: -12px; }
  }
</style>
